---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import StatusPill from '../components/StatusPill.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Chris Bell"
  description="I build the data infrastructure layer that other products depend on — and I think a lot about what it takes for organizations to actually use what gets built."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-80"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(221,211,198,.45) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(rgba(221,211,198,.45) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 72px 72px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto grid min-h-[calc(100vh-73px)] max-w-6xl items-center px-6 py-16 md:px-10 md:py-20">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.05fr)_minmax(340px,.72fr)] lg:gap-16">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-5 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase text-accent">
            AI, data platforms, product leadership
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-display text-[4rem] font-semibold leading-[0.9] text-ink md:text-[6.75rem]">
            Chris J. Bell
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-ink-muted md:text-2xl">
            I build platform products that make complex data trustworthy enough for real work,
            and help organizations absorb the change that follows.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/projects"
              class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-[6px] border border-accent bg-accent px-5 text-sm font-bold text-surface transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-accent-dark"
            >
              View projects
            </a>
            <a
              href="/about"
              class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-[6px] border border-accent bg-surface/60 px-5 text-sm font-bold text-accent transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-accent-light"
            >
              Read about the work
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="rounded-[8px] border border-border bg-surface/85 p-6 shadow-[0_22px_70px_rgba(26,26,26,0.08)]">
          <p class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase text-accent">Focus</p>
          <p class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink">
            Data trust, product systems, organizational adoption.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="mt-6 inline-flex text-sm font-bold text-accent transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-ink"
          >
            Read how I work &rarr;
          </a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-b border-border py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="mb-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,.7fr)_minmax(0,.75fr)] md:items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-4 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase text-accent">Featured project</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-5xl font-semibold leading-none text-ink md:text-7xl">
            Kate brings method to career coaching.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
          The homepage gives Kate more presence without turning the whole site into a product
          landing page. The portfolio still reads as Chris first, with projects as proof.
        </p>
      </div>

      <article class="grid overflow-hidden rounded-[8px] border border-border bg-surface md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,.65fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
        <div class="flex min-h-72 flex-col justify-between bg-accent p-8 text-surface md:p-10">
          <div class="font-display text-8xl font-semibold leading-none md:text-[8rem]">Kate</div>
          <p class="max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-surface/80">
            AI coaching built around structured assessment, role fit, interview prep, and a
            persistent working memory.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-8 md:p-12">
          <StatusPill status="Beta" />
          <h3 class="mt-6 max-w-2xl font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink md:text-5xl">
            Career coaching with rigor, not generic encouragement.
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
            Kate interviews you, keeps structured session files, and helps turn your actual
            experience into clear positioning for the roles you are pursuing.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/projects/kate"
            class="mt-7 text-sm font-bold text-accent transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-ink"
          >
            Explore Kate &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-b border-border py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="mb-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,.7fr)_minmax(0,.75fr)]">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-4 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase text-accent">Selected work</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-5xl font-semibold leading-none text-ink md:text-7xl">
            Small systems with a point of view.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
          AI agents, data tools, and product experiments that start from a concrete workflow
          instead of a generic demo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/projects/kate" class="group flex min-h-72 flex-col justify-between rounded-[8px] border border-border bg-surface p-7 transition-colors duration-150 hover:border-accent">
          <div>
            <div class="mb-5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-bold text-ink-muted">
              <span>AI agent</span>
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-gold"></span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-accent">Kate</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
              A coaching agent for senior job seekers, built around fit assessment, story
              development, research, and interview debriefs.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent group-hover:text-ink">View project &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/projects/whoop-mcp" class="group flex min-h-72 flex-col justify-between rounded-[8px] border border-border bg-surface p-7 transition-colors duration-150 hover:border-accent">
          <div>
            <div class="mb-5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-bold text-ink-muted">
              <span>Open source</span>
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate"></span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-accent">Whoop MCP</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
              A local bridge between Whoop data and AI agents, exposing recovery, sleep,
              strain, and workouts through typed MCP tools.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent group-hover:text-ink">View project &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/projects/cadence" class="group flex min-h-72 flex-col justify-between rounded-[8px] border border-border bg-surface p-7 transition-colors duration-150 hover:border-accent">
          <div>
            <div class="mb-5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-bold text-ink-muted">
              <span>Training coach</span>
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-sage"></span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-accent">Cadence</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
              Strength programming delivered to your phone. Endurance coaching grounded in your recovery data.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent group-hover:text-ink">View project &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
